snippet: The Red Bull driver Sebastian Vettel won the Japanese Grand Prix, but he will have to wait to clinch a fourth straight Formula One title.
abstract: Red Bull driver Sebastian Vettel wins Japanese Grand Prix in Formula One auto racing.
lead_paragraph: The Red Bull driver Sebastian Vettel won the Japanese Grand Prix, but he will have to wait to clinch a fourth straight Formula One title.

headline.main: Vettel Prevails in Japanese Grand Prix
